results.deck: Now Production Co., Ltd. is a Japanese game development/outsourcing studio.
results.description:
Overview

Now Production Co., Ltd. is a large development/outsourcing studio based in Japan. Now Production Co., Ltd. was founded in 1986. Now Production Co., Ltd. has worked with many of the big Japanese companies such as: Namco, Hudson, Capcom, Sega, Square, Konami, Nintendo, and more.
